reviews.text: I travel through here every day staff are awesome. One does look a bit grumpy but hes a nice guy. 🙌
Train station was closed no worning guy behind the desk was horrible no need for such insults

Busy commuter Station with town atmosphere at one end, country at the other and pleasant views down the line to Kirkby in summer.  Covered, though not fully enclosed waiting areas and lifts as well as ramps down to both platforms from station entrance. No park and ride facilities but bike rack on westbound platform. Pleasant and helpful staff.

N.B. If picking up or dropping off passengers by car the side streets to the north of the adjacent dual carriageway offer the safest and most convenient location.
